Package: scballpack
Type: Package
Title: Visualization Of T-cell Clonal Clusters
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Qile Yang, Ben Murrell
Authors@R: c(
    person("Qile", "Yang", email = "qile0317@gmail.com", role = c("cre","aut")),
    person("Ben", "Murrell", email = "benjamin.murrell@ki.se", role = "aut"))
Maintainer: Qile Yang <qile0317@gmail.com>
Description: A simple, customizable plotting API to visualize T-cell clonal expansion within sc-RNAseq clusters, 
    loosely based on delaunay trianglulation, improved from an original julia script by Ben Murrell APackOfTheClones.jl. 
    Imput data consists of a Seurat object with readily avaliable UMAP and cluster information, and an integrated T-cell repertoire.
    Additional manual labelling is possible of each cluster, and accepted overlap between clusters is also customizable.
